ansparent [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8"><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><h1 class="text-text-100 mt-3 -mb-1 text-[1.375rem] font-bold">GridSense Project — Step 1: Environment Setup &amp; GitHub Repo</h1>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Kamal, sab kuch padh liya. Solid project plan hai — chalte hain Step 1 se. Main tumhara mentor hun, har cheez explain karunga.</p>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<h2 class="text-text-100 mt-3 -mb-1 text-[1.125rem] font-bold">Step 1 ka Plan</h2>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Step 1 mein yeh 4 kaam honge:</p>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Project folder structure banana</strong> locally</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>GitHub repo banana</strong> aur connect karna</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Python virtual environment setup</strong> karna (backend ke liye)</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Node.js project initialize</strong> karna (frontend ke liye)</li>
</ol>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<h2 class="text-text-100 mt-3 -mb-1 text-[1.125rem] font-bold">1A — GitHub Repo Banao</h2>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Pehle GitHub pe repo create karo:</p>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">GitHub.com pe jao → <strong>New Repository</strong></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Name: <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">gridsense</code></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Description: <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">Real-Time Industrial Energy Intelligence Platform</code></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Public</strong> rakho (employers dekhenge)</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">✅ Add README.md check karo</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>.gitignore</strong> → Python select karo</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Create repository</strong> click karo</li>
</ol>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Phir "Code" button se HTTPS URL copy karo. Format hoga:</p>
