<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Ab API key lena hai. Yeh steps karo:</p>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">transparency.entsoe.eu</code> pe <strong>Login</strong> karo apne account se</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Login hone ke baad <strong>upar right corner</strong> mein apna naam dikhega — us pe click karo</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>"My Account Settings"</strong> option aayega — click karo</li>
</ol>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Dikh raha hai? Batao. 👍</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="flex justify-start opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-within:opacity-100 transition" role="group" aria-label="Message actions"><div class="text-text-300"><div class="text-text-300 flex items-stretch justify-between"><div class="w-fit" data-state="closed"><button class="inline-flex
