<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Dekho kya dikh raha hai:</p>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>GridSense API 1.0.0</strong> ✅</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Real-Time Industrial Energy Intelligence Platform</strong> ✅</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>GET /</strong> — Root route ✅</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>GET /health</strong> — Health route ✅</li>
</ul>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Yeh FastAPI ka <strong>Swagger UI</strong> hai — automatically hamare saare API routes document karta hai. Bahut professional lagta hai!</p>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Ab GitHub pe push karte hain. Terminal mein <strong>Ctrl+C</strong> dabao — server band karo.</p>
