 description nahi hona cahiye? like ki ye project kya problmes solve karenge and etc.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="flex justify-start opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-within:opacity-100 transition" role="group" aria-label="Message actions"><div class="text-text-300"><div class="text-text-300 flex items-stretch justify-between"><span class="text-text-500 text-xs flex items-center mr-2" data-state="closed">Apr 6</span><div class="flex items-center"><div class="w-fit" data-state="closed"><button class="inline-flex
