<div class="overflow-x-auto w-full px-2 mb-6"><table class="min-w-full border-collapse text-sm leading-[1.7] whitespace-normal"><thead class="text-left"><tr><th scope="col" class="text-text-100 border-b-0.5 border-border-300/60 py-2 pr-4 align-top font-bold">Code</th><th scope="col" class="text-text-100 border-b-0.5 border-border-300/60 py-2 pr-4 align-top font-bold">Kya kaam karta hai</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top"><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">load_dotenv()</code></td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top"><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">.env</code> file ki values ko memory mein load karta hai</td></tr><tr><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top"><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">FastAPI(...)</code></td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">Hamare API ka main object banata hai — title, description sab</td></tr><tr><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top"><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">CORSMiddleware</code></td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">Frontend (Next.js) ko backend se baat karne deta hai — browser by default block karta hai cross-origin requests</td></tr><tr><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top"><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">@app.get("/")</code></td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">Jab koi <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">http://localhost:8000/</code> khole toh yeh function run hoga</td></tr><tr><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top"><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">@app.get("/health")</code></td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">Server check karne ke liye — deployment mein kaam aata hai</td></tr></tbody></table></div>
