</ul>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">http://127.0.0.1:8000/docs</code> pe <strong>Swagger UI</strong> automatically bana — FastAPI ki best feature hai. Har API route automatically document ho jaata hai bina kuch alag likhe.</p>
