<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Ab <strong>Step 4 — Data Fetcher</strong> shuru karte hain.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">ENTSO-E API key abhi nahi mili — toh hum <strong>Open-Meteo API</strong> se shuru karte hain. Yeh free hai, koi API key nahi chahiye, aur weather data deta hai jo hamare project mein use hoga.</p>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>Pehle terminal mein server band karo — Ctrl+C dabao.</strong></p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Ho gaya? Batao. 👍</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="flex justify-start opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-within:opacity-100 transition" role="group" aria-label="Message actions"><div class="text-text-300"><div class="text-text-300 flex items-stretch justify-between"><div class="w-fit" data-state="closed"><button class="inline-flex
