ansparent [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8"><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Bilkul! Pehle deployment karte hain.</p>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>Step 9 — Deployment</strong></p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">2 cheezein deploy karni hain:</p>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Frontend</strong> → Vercel pe (Next.js)</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Backend</strong> → Render.com pe (FastAPI)</li>
</ul>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Pehle <strong>Backend — Render.com</strong> se shuru karte hain.</p>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Ek important kaam pehle karna hai — <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">backend/requirements.txt</code> update karna hai kyunki Render ko yeh file chahiye hogi.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Pehle backend folder mein jao aur venv activate karo:</p>
