ansparent [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8"><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Samajh gaya! Tum <strong>PWA (Progressive Web App)</strong> ki baat kar rahe ho.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">PWA matlab — website ko phone pe install kar sako, aur bilkul app ki tarah use karo. Home screen pe icon aata hai, fullscreen mein khulta hai.</p>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Yeh bahut easy hai Next.js mein. Ek package install karna hoga.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Pehle <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">frontend</code> folder mein jao:</p>
