ansparent [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8"><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Bilkul! Day 3 post mein PWA feature add karte hain.</p></div></div><div class="pl-2 pt-1 pb-2"><div class="font-ui bg-bg-000 rounded-2xl rounded-t-3xl overflow-hidden border-border-300 border -mx-1 mb-4 transition-colors focus-within:border-accent-200/50 focus-within:shadow-md"><div class="flex flex-col"><div class="overflow-y-auto max-h-[400px]"><div style="opacity: 1; filter: blur(0px); transform: none;"><textarea placeholder="Write your message..." class="px-5 pt-4 pb-4 w-full resize-none bg-transparent border-none text-sm text-text-100 placeholder:text-text-500 !outline-none !ring-0" style="field-sizing: content; min-height: 200px;">Day 3 : GridSense — Fully Deployed + PWA Ready.

GridSense is now live on the internet and installable as a mobile app.

Live URL: https://gridsense-eight.vercel.app

What I built today:
- GridSense dashboard UI with Next.js and Tailwind CSS
- Real-time energy charts using Recharts
- Live weather cards for European cities
- Deployed backend on Render.com
- Deployed frontend on Vercel
- PWA support — install GridSense on your phone like a native app

What the dashboard shows right now:
- Germany: 45,668 MW live load
- France: 43,041 MW live load
- Spain: 23,400 MW live load
- Poland: 18,805 MW live load
- Last 24hr energy load chart per country
- Live weather for Berlin, Paris, Madrid, Warsaw

Data sources:
- ENTSO-E API — official European electricity data
- Open-Meteo API — live weather data

Tech Stack:
- Frontend: Next.js, Tailwind CSS, Recharts
- Backend: Python, FastAPI
- Data: ENTSO-E API, Open-Meteo API
- Deployment: Vercel + Render.com

GitHub: https://github.com/kamal-lochan-sahu/gridsense
Live: https://gridsense-eight.vercel.app

Project-2 Status: In Progress

#Python #FastAPI #NextJS #PWA #EnergyTech #Industry40 #MachineLearning #100DaysOfCode #OpenToWork</textarea></div></div><div class="flex items-center justify-end gap-2 px-2 py-2"><div class="flex items-center h-8 bg-bg-000 rounded-lg border-0.5 border-border-300 shadow-sm overflow-hidden"><div class="w-fit" data-state="closed"><button class="inline-flex
